cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CL 

This paper focuses on the task of real-time semantic segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a neural network architecture (cs.LG) that incorporates multi-resolution branches and a cascade feature fusion unit. The paper also discusses the use of label guidance to reduce computation (cs.AI) and evaluates the method on challenging datasets (cs.MM, cs.CL).
